<typeStatus id="5C551DCDFFBFFFC2FD14FE62B77DFD83" box="[763,866,500,527]" pageId="6" pageNumber="211">holotype</typeStatus>
female from Meru Mountain (
<collectingCountry id="FBF9E3FFFFBFFFC2FF40FD82B53CFDA3" box="[175,291,532,559]" name="Tanzania" pageId="6" pageNumber="211">Tanzania</collectingCountry>
). Judging from the figure of the epigyne, it is misplaced in 
<taxonomicName id="44EED8ECFFBFFFC2FC24FD83B017FDA2" baseAuthorityName="WSC" baseAuthorityYear="2017" box="[971,1032,533,558]" class="Arachnida" family="Tetragnathidae" genus="Meta" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="6" pageNumber="211" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
